                <b>Tofu</b> - primary compute node, great performance for game servers, docker containers, websites and other miscellaneous services.
                
                <br><br>
                <b>CPU:</b> Ryzen 5 5500 (3.6GHz, 6c 12t)
                <br>
                <b>Memory/RAM:</b> 32GB DDR4 3200Mhz
