                <h3 class="box-text frontpage-text-small">Network, monitoring and backups</h3>
                <p class="box-text">
                Systems are connected to the internet via fttp , nodes have their own static ip address protected with <a class="link-text" href="https://globalsecurelayer.com" target="_blank">gsl ddos protection</a>.

                <br><br>
                Nodes are monitored with <a class="link-text" href="https://hetrixtools" target="_blank">hetrixtools</a> in combination with <a class="link-text" href="https://ntfy.sh" target="_blank">ntfy</a> to monitor uptime, cpu, ram, storage and bandwidth usage.

                <br><br>
                Encrypted backups of server disks are sent to <a class="link-text" href="https://wasabi.com" target="_blank">wasabi</a>.

